Being part of a unique and exclusive Luxury Brand, it is a must that you bring with you a minimum of three years 5* hotel experience, fluency in English. Arabic or Italian speaking candidates are sincerely encouraged to apply.
At Armani Hotels & Resorts we are dedicated to nurturing our employees natural talent; being an Ambassador of the Armani Brand we are seeking individuals to work with 'the right attitude', demonstrating sincere, respectful and warm hearted service. Precisely and confidently you will work with us cultivating our multi skilled and empowered Teams.
If you want to be associated with the a state of the art unique fitness concept situated alongside the tallest tower in the world and have an innate interest in fitness, and consider yourself to be part of the fitness elite leading a lifestyle of health and fitness we are interested to know more about you.
The ideal candidate must be dynamic, service minded, organised, concern for quality and an eye for details, result driven, customer focus,and effective communication skills
